name: Andrew Ho
description:
Andrew joins The Data School with more than 10 years of extensive customer service experience in hospitality and administration fields, even owning and operating his own coffee shop at one point. Having identified a newfound interest in Tableau, Andrew is now taking his skills into data analytics. 

Outside of work, Andrew enjoys spending his time pampering his dog and two cats. He enjoys and appreciates all kinds of food, so you can be rest assured that no food will go to waste.
